welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Port Townsend, a charming coastal town known for its Victorian architecture and rich history. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all the beauty and charm this city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport handles all commercial flights and houses various amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The General Aviation Terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport serves private and chartered flights, offering a comfortable and convenient experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Skagit Regional Airport provides efficient handling and processing of air freight and cargo.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
